    {
      "id": "PopularPost270995",
      "post_content": "This card *can* be phenomenal in constructed if you build around it, but probably not too exciting otherwise.  \n  \nFirst of all, this card is super annoying for your opponent. Unless they have a 0/5+ creature to block with, there's a risk it will wipe out most of their critters when they do. If they don't like that possibility, they have to let it through and take 4. And they can't chump it, or else they take trample damage plus the detonation risk. And they have to make this decision *every turn*. I love the dynamic.  \n  \nBut it doesn't have to be annoying for you -- put a lot of undying and indestructible creatures in your deck ([Warden of the Wall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warden of the Wall) is pretty good here). It fits quite nicely in the mana curve right below [Stuffy Doll](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stuffy Doll). Now your opponent has to decide whether to take 4 now, or risk taking 8 + trample when they block.   \n  ",
      "posted_by": "mathy1863",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost270995\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">This card <i>can</i> be phenomenal in constructed if you build around it, but probably not too exciting otherwise.<br/><br/>First of all, this card is super annoying for your opponent.  Unless they have a 0/5+ creature to block with, there's a risk it will wipe out most of their critters when they do.  If they don't like that possibility, they have to let it through and take 4.  And they can't chump it, or else they take trample damage plus the detonation risk.  And they have to make this decision <i>every turn</i>.  I love the dynamic.<br/><br/>But it doesn't have to be annoying for you -- put a lot of undying and indestructible creatures in your deck (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Warden of the Wall\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warden of the Wall\">Warden of the Wall</a> is pretty good here).  It fits quite nicely in the mana curve right below <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stuffy Doll\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stuffy Doll\">Stuffy Doll</a>.  Now your opponent has to decide whether to take 4 now, or risk taking 8 + trample when they block.  <br/><br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '270995'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy88229\">mathy1863</span>\r\n                                (9/26/2012 9:10:18 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
